// since May 2026. This file remains for historical reference and may
// be deleted in a future cleanup pass. Do not edit and deploy from
// here — changes will not propagate to production.
//
// Deploy workflow: paste-replace into the Firebase Console (canonical),
// or `firebase deploy --only firestore:rules --project spert-suite`
// from the Landing Page repo (fallback). See the canonical guide at
// /Users/william/Documents/SPERT Documentation/cloud-storage-guide/ARCHITECTURE.md
